I"Ê<p>Relationships come to an end for many reasons. They may end out of personal choice or for reasons outside of our control.</p>

<p>Ending relationships can be difficult if you feel a sense of loyalty for the other person or if you have been avoiding ending the relationship out of fear of the consequences.</p>

<p>Consciously ending a relationship in a healthy way is a skill that you can develop which can have benefits for your emotional wellbeing.</p>
